org.apache.ctakes.smokingstatus.ae

Class ResolutionAnnotator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.smokingstatus.ae.ResolutionAnnotator

  • public class ResolutionAnnotator
extends Object
    Resolves the data produced by the KU classifier, negation detection, and PCS classifier into a single smoking status value for the given sentence. The old NominalAttributeValue objects are removed and replaced with a single NominalAttributeValue object that represents the final classification.
    Author:
    Mayo Clinic
